                                <h2>Lists <a href="" id="Lists" class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                <p>All lists, including <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>, and <code>&lt;dl&gt;</code>, have a margin-bottom of 1rem and a margin-top that has been eliminated. There is no margin-bottom for nested lists. On the <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> elements, the <code>padding-left</code> has also been reset.</p>

