                                <p class="mt-20">
                                Description lists now have improved margins for a cleaner design, more obvious hierarchy, and better spacing. <code>&lt;dd&gt;</code>s add <code>margin-bottom:</code> <code>.5rem</code> and reset <code>margin-left</code> to 0, whereas <code>&lt;dt&gt;</code>s are <strong>bolded</strong>.
                                </p>

